This study will examine the effects of six week dance training, using the Xbox Kinect Just Dance 2014 programme, on the agility scores along with general and hamstring flexibility and extensibility of the hip flexor.

 The effects of the dance programme will be compared with those of proven agility training techniques (ladder drills).

